title: What is an original print?
creator_credit: RATAS Arts Consultancy and Oxide City Productions
brief_description: A guide to the processes and techniques of original printmaking. Demonstrates relief prints (woodcuts, linocuts), incised or intaglio prints (engravings, etchings), lithography and serigraphy (silkscreen). Presented by Josef Lebovic.
